Shrubbery can be installed with a simple::

    python setup.py install

You'll need BeautifulSoup_ too. If you have EasyInstall_ installed, just type::

    easy_install shrubbery

And you're all set.

_EasyInstall: http://www.crummy.com/software/BeautifulSoup/
_BeautifulSoup: http://peak.telecommunity.com/DevCenter/EasyInstall
